message.entry: Invalid task name ''{0}''. Task name segments must contain only letters, digits, underscores, dashes, and periods, and must not start with a dash. Separate multiple segments in task names with a colon, for example, “mygroup:mytask”.
Array of tasks must either be the same size as the array of task names or be a scalar.
无法添加任务，因为父级不支持分组任务。
